  "instructions": [
    "Marinate the pork shoulder in a mixture of lemon juice, orange juice, honey, pomegranate molasses, and pork stock for at least 2 hours.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the pork shoulder and sear until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the juniper berries, thyme, and rosemary to the wok and stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the pork stock and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 1 hour.",
    "Transfer the pork to a serving dish and garnish with fresh herbs.",
    "Serve the pork with the sauce spooned over the top."
